item.title: US Stocks Picked
item.description: WBA (Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.) Middle Walgreens Boots Alliance has beaten recent earnings expectations, but faces risks due to a challenging retail environment and the toll of healthcare transformation. The company continues to navigate through these challenges by cutting costs and focusing on the performance of its US Retail Pharmacy segment.
